implements ProtobufRpcEngine.RpcWrapper
    Wrapper for Protocol Buffer Requests Note while this wrapper is writable, the request on the wire is in Protobuf. Several methods on and RPC use type Writable as a wrapper to work across multiple RpcEngine kinds.
